 <span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Filtro_de_Option"> Filtro de Option </sp=
an></h2>
<pre>sip.CSeq.method =3D=3D "OPTIONS"</pre>
<h2><span class=3D"editsection">[<a href=3D"http://10.3.1.52/telefonia/inde=
x.php?title=3DWireshark_-_Filtros_para_Wireshark&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;sect=
ion=3D2" title=3D"Editar secci=C3=B3n: Filtro de ANI">editar</a>]</span> <s=
pan class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Filtro_de_ANI"> Filtro de ANI </span></h2>
<pre>sip.from.user contains "43897001" and not icmp</pre>
<h2><span class=3D"editsection">[<a href=3D"http://10.3.1.52/telefonia/inde=
x.php?title=3DWireshark_-_Filtros_para_Wireshark&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;sect=
ion=3D3" title=3D"Editar secci=C3=B3n: Filtro de To">editar</a>]</span> <sp=
an class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Filtro_de_To"> Filtro de To </span></h2>
<pre>sip.To contains "5402290" and not icmp
</pre>
<h2><span class=3D"editsection">[<a href=3D"http://10.3.1.52/telefonia/inde=
x.php?title=3DWireshark_-_Filtros_para_Wireshark&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;sect=
ion=3D4" title=3D"Editar secci=C3=B3n: Filtro de URI">editar</a>]</span> <s=
pan class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Filtro_de_URI"> Filtro de URI </span></h2>
<pre>sip.r-uri  contains "sip:5402290@172.22.181.18:5060" and not icmp
</pre>
<h2><span class=3D"editsection">[<a href=3D"http://10.3.1.52/telefonia/inde=
x.php?title=3DWireshark_-_Filtros_para_Wireshark&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;sect=
ion=3D5" title=3D"Editar secci=C3=B3n: Filtro captura por host">editar</a>]=
</span> <span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Filtro_captura_por_host"> Filtro =
captura por host </span></h2>
<p>Ejemplo para captura de TIGO Outbound en el servidor de capturas 10.3.1.=
50 interface eno2
</p>
<pre>host 10.1.8.1 or host 190.248.166 or host 10.1.8.134 or host 10.1.8.13=
8 or host 10.1.8.136 or host 10.1.8.39 or host 10.1.8.40 or host 10.1.8.45 =
or host 10.1.8.46 or host 10.1.8.137 or host 10.1.8.12 or host 10.1.8.139 o=
r host 10.1.8.13 or host 10.1.8.21 or host 10.1.8.23 or host 10.1.8.28 or h=
ost 10.1.8.31 or host 10.1.8.30 and not (net 10.3.1.0/24 or net 10.3.2.0/25=
 or net 10.1.10.128/25 or 10.1.8.143 or 10.1.8.152 or 10.1.8.153 or 10.1.8.=
154 or 10.1.8.144 or 10.1.8.145 or 10.1.8.146 or 10.1.8.149 or 10.1.8.155 o=
r 10.1.8.156 or 10.1.8.157 or 10.1.8.158 or 10.1.8.159 or 10.1.8.147 or 10.=
1.8.148 or 10.1.8.150 or 10.1.8.151 or 10.1.8.10)
</pre>
<p>Ejemplo para capturar GVP, todos los componentes de genesys:
</p>
<pre>host 10.1.8.141 or host 10.1.8.142 or host 10.1.8.143 or host 10.1.8.1=
47 or host 10.1.8.148 or host 10.1.8.150 or host 10.1.8.151 or host 10.1.8.=
152 or host 10.1.8.153 or host 10.1.8.154 or host 10.1.8.144 or host 10.1.8=
.145 or host 10.1.8.146 or host 10.1.8.149 or host 10.1.8.155 or host 10.1.=
8.156 or host 10.1.8.10 or host 10.1.8.44
</pre>
<p><a rel=3D"nofollow" class=3D"external free" href=3D"https://wiki.wiresha=
rk.org/CaptureFilters">https://wiki.wireshark.org/CaptureFilters</a>
</p>
<h2><span class=3D"editsection">[<a href=3D"http://10.3.1.52/telefonia/inde=
x.php?title=3DWireshark_-_Filtros_para_Wireshark&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;sect=
ion=3D6" title=3D"Editar secci=C3=B3n: Filtro IVR con RTP solo SBC TIGO">ed=
itar</a>]</span> <span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Filtro_IVR_con_RTP_solo_=
SBC_TIGO"> Filtro IVR con RTP solo SBC TIGO </span></h2>
<pre>host 190.248.66.171 or host 190.248.66.166 and not net 10.3.0.0/16 and=
 not net 10.1.10.0/25 and not host 10.1.8.1
</pre>

